        <mxCell id="benefits" value="ðŸŽ¯ Why Service B Federates from Service A:&#xa;&#xa;âœ… Payment team needs database context:&#xa;   â€¢ Slow payments â†’ Check DB query time&#xa;   â€¢ Payment errors â†’ Check DB connections&#xa;   â€¢ Performance issues â†’ Check DB load&#xa;&#xa;âœ… Unified alerting in Payment Prometheus:&#xa;   â€¢ Alert: High payment errors + DB issues&#xa;   â€¢ Alert: Slow API + High DB query time&#xa;&#xa;âœ… Single dashboard for Payment team:&#xa;   â€¢ Payment metrics + DB performance&#xa;   â€¢ No need to access Database team's Prometheus" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
